name: testTheme
css: .fh_appform_container .fh_appform_button_navigation{background-color:#11d628;border: 1px solid #11d628;font-size:12pt;font-family:arial;color:#516aa0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;border-radius:5px;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_button_navigation:active{background-color:#b12b4a;border: .fh_appform_button_action.special_button{width:100%;margin-top:10px;line-height:28px;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_button_action.special_button.fh_appform_removeInputBtn{width:50%;margin-top:10px;line-height:28px;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_button_cancel:active{background-color:#3c0b82;border: 1px solid #3c0b82;font-size:12pt;font-family:arial;color:#516aa0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;border-radius:5px;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_navigation{background-color:#d41bcd;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_header{background-color:#15a47c;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_body{background-color:#6a2f55;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_form{background-color:#5fbd28;border:none;padding:5px;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_field_title{font-size:14pt;font-family:arial;color:#8bf27a;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;display:block;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_field_title.fh_appform_field_numbering{display:inline-block;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_field_area{background-color:#bda17a;border-width:thick;border-style:double;border-color:#d53160;padding:5px;border-bottom:none;border-radius:5px;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_field_area:last-child{border-width:thick;border-style:double;border-color:#d53160;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_field_area.fh_appform_field_section_break{border:none;background:transparent;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_field_input{background-color:#d7cad3;font-size:14pt;font-family:arial;color:#770238;font-style:italic;font-weight:normal;border-width:thick;border-style:double;border-color:#a72921;width:100%;border-radius:5px;line-height:1.4em;padding:5px 0px 5px 5px;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_field_input .radio{margin-right:10px;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_field_input .checkbox{margin-right:10px;display:inline;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_field_input .choice{margin-right:10px;display:inline;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_field_instructions{background-color:#2edc3b;font-size:12pt;font-family:arial;color:#53841e;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;border-width:thick;border-style:double;border-color:#59089e;margin-bottom:10px;border-radius:5px;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_title{font-size:18pt;font-family:arial;color:#34cf75;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;text-align:center;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_description{font-size:14pt;font-family:arial;color:#058df6;font-style:italic;font-weight:normal;text-align:center;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_error{font-size:12pt;font-family:arial;color:#ca2853;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;background-color:#b33265;border-width:thick;border-style:double;border-color:#65e116;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_field_section_break_title{font-size:14pt;font-family:arial;color:#2cec09;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;text-align:center;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_page_title{font-size:11pt;font-family:arial;color:#64f53c;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-align:center;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_progress_wrapper{padding-top:20px;padding-bottom:10px;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_progress_steps{background-color:#0f87ae;border-width:thick;border-style:double;border-color:#f05444;width:100%;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_progress_steps td{text-align:center;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_progress_steps td.active .fh_appform_page_title{text-align:center;display:inline;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_progress_steps .fh_appform_page_title{padding-left:10px;display:none;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_progress_steps .number{padding-top:4px;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_progress_steps .number_container{background-color:#6f824f;border-width:thick;border-style:double;border-color:#bdeaa2;font-size:11pt;font-family:arial;color:#e31610;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;display:inline-block;border-radius:13px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_progress_steps td.active .number_container{background-color:#b10b77;border-width:thick;border-style:double;border-color:#5363c1;font-size:11pt;font-family:arial;color:#2fbdbd;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_field_required:first-child:after{color: #92b37a;content:' *';display:inline;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_action_bar{padding:18px 20px 18px 20px;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_action_bar button.fh_appform_two_button{width:50%;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_action_bar button.fh_appform_three_button{width:33.3%;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_section_area{background-color:#12337a;padding:5px;border-radius:5px;margin-top:5px;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_hidden{display:none;}.fh_appform_container .fh_appform_logo{background-image: url("data:image/jpeg;base64,");height: 100px;width:100px;background-position:center;background-repeat:no-repeat;width:100%;}
